Our Commitment to you
At PlayIn Radio we are committed to the fundamental right to the protection of your personal data.
We appreciate that you put your trust in us when you provide us with your information and we do not take this lightly.
We ensure your privacy is protected
. We guarantee compliance with current data protection legislation, and take a proactive data protection approach with regard to the services we provide.
We strive to be transparent in the way we process your data
. We have written our Privacy Policy and related documents in plain language. We want you to read our policies and understand our privacy practices.
