Second Layer of Information
Summary
We are committed to the fundamental right to the protection of your personal data. PlayIn Radio guarantees compliance with current data protection legislation, including General Data Protection Regulation (“
GDPR
”), the comprehensive privacy legislation of the EU. We also are fully compliant with Spanish regulations on the protection of personal data, reflected in Organic Law 3/2018, of December 5, Protection of Personal Data and Guarantee of Digital Rights.
The Policy also explains your rights and choices with respect to your personal information, and how you can contact us if you have any questions or concerns. No part of the Services is directed to children under the age of 14, nor do we knowingly collect information from anyone under the age of 14. This Policy does not apply to other websites, mobile applications and services provided by PlayIn Radio. Please visit the privacy policy for the respective website, mobile application or service.
This privacy policy is intended to inform you about your rights under the GDPR.
Your use of the Services is subject to this Policy and the
Terms of Service
accessible on the App or Site.
